columns = []
	
	instanceNameCol = self.getChild("root").GetDefaultColumn(Field='InstanceName',Header='Instance',Render='string')
	columns.append(instanceNameCol)

	instanceTagPathCol = self.getChild("root").GetDefaultColumn(Field='InstanceFullPath',Header='Tag Path',Render='string')
	instanceTagPathCol['visible'] = False
	columns.append(instanceTagPathCol)
	
	alarms = value.values()[0]['Configuration']
	alarmsColumns = []
	for alarm in alarms:
		field = alarm
		dataType = alarms[alarm]['DataType']
		if dataType == 'Boolean':
			render = 'boolean'
		else:
			render = 'number'
			
		alarmFullPath = alarms[alarm]['FullPath']
		tagPathDocumentation = alarmFullPath+ ".Documentation"
		tagPathDocumentationOrder = alarmFullPath + ".DocumentationOrder"
		metadata = system.tag.readBlocking(tagPaths=[tagPathDocumentation,tagPathDocumentationOrder])
		
		header = metadata[0].value
		documentationOrder = metadata[1].value
		
		alarmCol = self.getChild("root").GetDefaultColumn(Field=field,Header=header,Render=render)
		alarmCol['documentationOrder'] = documentationOrder
		alarmsColumns.append(alarmCol)
	alarmsColumns = sorted(alarmsColumns,key=lambda row: row['documentationOrder'],reverse=False)
	columns.extend(alarmsColumns)
	return columns

data = []
	for module in value:
		instanseName = module['Name']
		instanceFullPath = module['InstanceFullPath']
		
		alarms =  module['Alarms']
		for alarm in alarms:
			row = {}
			row['InstanceName'] = instanseName
			row['InstanceFullPath'] = instanceFullPath
			configuration = alarms[alarm]['Configuration']
			alarmName = alarm
			row['Alarm'] = alarmName
			for cfg in configuration:
				configurationName = cfg
				row[configurationName] = configuration[cfg]
			data.append(row)
	return data
